"title": "7245: Judah, kingdom of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7245: judah, kingdom of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The southernmost of the two kingdoms into which Israel split after the death of Solomon. It was ruled by a series of Davidic kings until the sixth century B.C., when it became a province of the Babylonian empire.</p>\n<h2>Origin of the kingdom of Judah</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs12:1-1Kgs12:24\">1KI 12:1–12:24</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr10:1-2Chr11:4\">2CH 10:1–11:4</a></p>\n<h2>Loss of the wealth amassed in Judah</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:25-1Kgs14:26\">1KI 14:25–14:26</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr12:9\">2CH 12:9</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:18-1Kgs15:19\">1KI 15:18–15:19</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:2-2Chr16:3\">2CH 16:2–16:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs12:17-2Kgs12:18\">2KI 12:17–12:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs14:14\">2KI 14:14</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr25:24\">2CH 25:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs16:8\">2KI 16:8</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr28:21\">2CH 28:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:14-2Kgs18:16\">2KI 18:14–18:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:23\">2CH 24:23</a></p>\n<h2>Apostasy in Judah</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:22-1Kgs14:24\">1KI 14:22–14:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs8:16-2Kgs8:19\">2KI 8:16–8:19</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr21:5-2Chr21:7\">2CH 21:5–21:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs16:10-2Kgs16:16\">2KI 16:10–16:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:2-2Kgs21:16\">2KI 21:2–21:16</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr33:2-2Chr33:10\">2CH 33:2–33:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr28:22-2Chr28:23\">2CH 28:22–28:23</a></p>\n<h2>Religious revival in Judah</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:2-2Kgs18:7\">2KI 18:2–18:7</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr29:1-2Chr29:2\">2CH 29:1–29:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:1\">2CH 31:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:20-2Chr31:21\">2CH 31:20–31:21</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs12:1-2Kgs12:16\">2KI 12:1–12:16</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:1-2Chr24:14\">2CH 24:1–24:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:1-2Kgs23:25\">2KI 23:1–23:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:1-2Chr34:13\">2CH 34:1–34:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:29-2Chr34:33\">2CH 34:29–34:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr29:1-2Chr31:1\">2CH 29:1–31:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr35:1-2Chr35:19\">2CH 35:1–35:19</a></p>\n<h2>The reign of Athaliah in Judah</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs11:1-2Kgs11:16\">2KI 11:1–11:16</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr22:10-2Chr23:21\">2CH 22:10–23:21</a></p>\n<h2>Coalitions between Judah and Israel</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs8:28-2Kgs8:29\">2KI 8:28–8:29</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr22:5-2Chr22:6\">2CH 22:5–22:6</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:1-1Kgs22:5\">1KI 22:1–22:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr18:1-2Chr18:3\">2CH 18:1–18:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs3:4-2Kgs3:7\">2KI 3:4–3:7</a></p>\n<h2>War in Judah</h2>\n<h3>With Israel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:6\">1KI 15:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:30\">1KI 14:30</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr12:15\">2CH 12:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:16-1Kgs15:17\">1KI 15:16–15:17</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:1\">2CH 16:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs14:8-2Kgs14:14\">2KI 14:8–14:14</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr25:17-2Chr25:24\">2CH 25:17–25:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs16:5\">2KI 16:5</a></p>\n<h3>With other nations</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs14:7\">2KI 14:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs8:20-2Kgs8:22\">2KI 8:20–8:22</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr21:8-2Chr21:10\">2CH 21:8–21:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:8\">2KI 18:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:13-2Kgs19:36\">2KI 18:13–19:36</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:9-2Chr32:19\">2CH 32:9–32:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa36:1-Isa36:22\">ISA 36:1–36:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr21:16-2Chr21:17\">2CH 21:16–21:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr25:11-2Chr25:12\">2CH 25:11–25:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr28:17-2Chr28:18\">2CH 28:17–28:18</a></p>\n<h2>Judah's loss of independence and change of status from kingdom to province</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:1-2Kgs25:12\">2KI 25:1–25:12</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:17-2Chr36:20\">2CH 36:17–36:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer39:1-Jer39:10\">JER 39:1–39:10</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:22-2Kgs25:24\">2KI 25:22–25:24</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer40:7-Jer40:9\">JER 40:7–40:9</a></p>",
